snippet: Natalie Coughlin and Missy Franklin had wins at the Santa Clara Grand Prix. Ryan Lochte won the 400 individual medley in a meet-record.
abstract: Swimmer Natalie Coughlin wins 50-meter freestyle and Missy Franklin takes the 200 freestyle and 200 backstroke in the Santa Clara Grand Prix in Santa Clara, Calif;  Ryan Lochte wins the 400 individual medley in a meet-record.
lead_paragraph: Natalie Coughlin and Missy Franklin had wins at the Santa Clara Grand Prix. Ryan Lochte won the 400 individual medley in a meet-record.

headline.main: Swimming Victories for Coughlin, Franklin and Lochte
headline.print_headline: Victories for Coughlin, Franklin and Lochte
